job.title: NIAB JRF Recruitment  2021 Apply Online for Various Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the post:

  • Junior Research Fellow

Description:

National Institute of Animal Biotechnology issued various vacancies for the posts of Junior Research Fellow. The online application for these posts under NIAB shall start from 19.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 30.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for NIAB JRF Recruitment 2021 :

  • Mode of application: Online
  • No Information Provided
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 19.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 30.04.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have completed in M.Pharma, M.Sc, M.E/M.Tech, MVSC  to apply for the post of Junior Research Fellow

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 21 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 30 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

NIAB Junior Research Fellow Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per the 7th pay commission for the post of Junior Research Fellow is INR 31000/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

How to apply for NIAB JRF Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of NIAB.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Junior Research Fellow.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
